<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Mapito.org</title>
	<% include ./partials/static-css-js %>
	<link href="/stylesheets/index.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<script src="/javascript/index.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<% include ./partials/googleanalytics %>

	<% include ./partials/header %>

	<div id="index-blue">
		<div class="container text-center">
			<h1>Welcome to Mapito.org!</h1>
			<div id="index-blue-text">
				Mapito.org is an open data and open source GIS system with an API that facilitates the development of Web services and Mobile Apps.
				Mapito.org is creating an abstraction layer above the generic services offered by the major web-based GIS systems, in order to facilitate the migration of the user applications to new services.
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


	<div id="options">
		<div class="container">
			<!-- Example row of columns -->
			<div class="row text-center">
				<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
					<h2>Maps</h2>
					<p>
						Mapito facilitates the creation and embedding of a map with custom controls.
						Mapito using multiple map services such as Google Maps and Bing Maps and allows the one-click switching between of these map services without affecting the previous settings.
						The system records the users activity on a map and stores it for later processing and analysis.
					</p>
					<p>
						<a class="btn btn-default" id="try-simple-maps" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".sign-up-modal">Try it &raquo;</a>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
					<h2>Route tracking</h2>
					<p>
						Route tracking is an additional feature of this system which allows to track routes through a web browser of a smartphone, tablet or any device with GPS and HTML5 Geolocation support.
						GPS Track Smoothing is an another useful feature provided by Mapito and designed to remove outliers in trace data.
					</p>
					<p>
						<a class="btn btn-default" id="try-gps-tracking" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".sign-up-modal">Try it &raquo;</a>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
					<h2>API</h2>
					<p>
						Mapito provides two APIs.
						A JavaScript API that's designed for developers who use embedded Mapito Maps and provides methods to edit the maps.
						A HTTP API which is designed for web and mobile developers and provides all options of Mapito via HTTP requests and more options, such as for storing and retrieving gps routes.
					</p>
					<p>
						<a class="btn btn-default" id="view-api" href="#"  data-toggle="modal" data-target=".sign-up-modal">View details &raquo;</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- /container -->
	</div>


	<div class="modal fade log-in-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="modal-dialog modal-sm modal-dialog-center">
			<div class="modal-content ">
				<div class="modal-body text-center">
					<div >
						<a href="/auth/facebook" class="btn btn-primary loginbtn">
							<span class="fa fa-facebook fa-lg loginicons"></span>
							<span>Log in with Facebook</span>
						</a>
						<a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-danger loginbtn">
							<span class="fa fa-google-plus fa-lg loginicons"></span>
							<span>Log in with Google+</span>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div>
						<a class="btn btn-warning loginbtn" id="log-in-with-mail-btn">
							<span class="fa fa-user loginicons"></span>
							<span>Log in with Email</span>
						</a>
						<div class="text-left" id="log-in-with-mail-form" style="display:none;">
							<hr>

							<div class="alert alert-warning" id="warnLogInMsg" role="alert" style="display:none;">Incorrect email or password.</div>

							<div class="alert alert-danger" id="errorLogInMsg" role="alert" style="display:none;">
								An unexpected error has occurred. Please try again later. <br> If this problem continues, please contact with system administrator.
							</div>

							<form action="/connect/local" method="post" id="sign-in-form">
								<div class="form-group" >
									<label>Email:</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="email">
								</div>
								<div class="form-group">
									<label>Password:</label>
									<input type="password" class="form-control" name="password">
								</div>

								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Login</button>
								<a href="#" data-dismiss="modal" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".forgot-password-modal">Forgot your password?</a>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-footer text-center">
					<span>Don't have an account? <a href="#" data-dismiss="modal" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".sign-up-modal">Sign up</a></span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="modal fade sign-up-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="modal-dialog modal-sm modal-dialog-center">
			<div class="modal-content ">
				<div class="modal-body text-center">
					<div >
						<a href="/auth/facebook" class="btn btn-primary loginbtn">
							<span class="fa fa-facebook fa-lg loginicons"></span>
							<span>Sign up with Facebook</span>
						</a>
						<a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-danger loginbtn">
							<span class="fa fa-google-plus fa-lg loginicons"></span>
							<span>Sign up with Google+</span>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div>
						<a class="btn btn-warning loginbtn" id="sign-up-with-mail-btn">
							<span class="fa fa-user loginicons"></span>
							<span>Sign up with Email</span>
						</a>
						<div class="text-left" id="sign-up-with-mail-form" style="display:none;">
							<hr>
							<div class="alert alert-warning" id="warnSignUpMsg" role="alert" style="display: none;">
								That email is already taken.
							</div>

							<div class="alert alert-danger" id="errorSignUpMsg" role="alert" style="display: none;">
								An unexpected error has occurred. Please try again later. <br>
								If this problem continues, please contact with system
								administrator.
							</div>

							<form action="/signup" method="post" id="sign-up-form">
								<div class="form-group" >
									<label for="name">Full name:</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" id="name">
									<p class="text-warning"></p>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group" >
									<label for="email">Email:</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="email">
									<p class="text-warning"></p>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="password">Password:</label>
									<input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" id="password">
									<label for="confirm-password">Confirm your password:</label>
									<input type="password" class="form-control" name="confirmpassword" id="confirm-password">
									<p class="text-warning"></p>
								</div>

								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Sign up</button>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-footer text-center">
					<span>Already have an account? <a href="#" data-dismiss="modal" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".log-in-modal">Login</a></span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="modal fade forgot-password-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="modal-dialog modal-sm modal-dialog-center">
			<div class="modal-content ">
				<div class="modal-body text-center">
					<div>
						<div class="modal-header">
							<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
							<h4 class="modal-title">Reset Password </h4>
						</div>
						<div class="text-left" id="forgot-password-form-div">

							<div class="alert alert-warning" id="warnForgotPasswordMsg" role="alert" style="display: none;">
								This email not exists.
							</div>

							<div class="alert alert-danger" id="errorForgotPasswordMsg" role="alert" style="display: none;">
								An unexpected error has occurred. Please try again later. <br>
								If this problem continues, please contact with system
								administrator.
							</div>
							<br>
							<p>
							Enter the email address associated with your account, and we'll email you a link to reset your password.
							</p>
							<form method="post" id="forgot-password-form">
								<div class="form-group" >
									<label for="email">Email:</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="reset-email">
									<p class="text-warning"></p>
								</div>

								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Submit</button>
							</form>
						</div>
						<div id="forgot-password-success-div" style="display:none;">
							<br>A link to reset your password has been sent to <span id="reset-password-email"></span>.
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-footer text-center">
					<span>Back to <a href="#" data-dismiss="modal" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".log-in-modal">Login</a></span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


