		<div class="container">
			<p>
				Mapito.org was created as part of the undergraduate thesis titled "Design and implementation of a web application for recording and analyzing usersâ€™ actions on digital geographical maps" in Department of Informatics, Ionian University, Corfu, Greece.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a class="github-icon" href="https://github.com/map1t0/mapito" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>
			</p>
			<p>
				Copyright &copy; 2015 Mapito.org
			</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
